{"tid":428480,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"Ps4 proclub 新組隊.","createTime":"2017-10-08T06:05:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-11T14:22:33.000Z","uid":117146,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"c14826c04c9aae329538e01c77887320563aaca7","tid":428480,"uid":117146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T06:05:21.000Z","msg":"大家好. <br />\n我相信大家有隊既都已經埋哂班<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n宜家想搵一d未埋班既球員組隊. <br />\n<br />\n要求好簡單: <br />\n1.) 重組織, 走位, 現位俾波, 多配合. <br />\n2.) 可以適當既上腳. (有d技術既球員, 利申: 我無技術可言<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n3.) 唔好太個人主義. <br />\n<br />\n乜位置都需要, 練波, PT亦可. (我打cdm, 同後衛的)<br />\n最緊要大家玩得開心, 相信如果大家玩得開心一定唔會離開球隊.<br />\n<br />\n先睇睇夠唔夠人先, 最理想計埋自己6-7人, 暫時. <br />\n<br />\n請大家多多指教, 一齊進步. <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"630c25b347bd8beee8bbf970afa5ac5a51e14c6b","tid":428480,"uid":115650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T06:08:55.000Z","msg":"pt 左\\右翼ok?<br />\n<br />\n我本身打開cdm，但想練下打翼，所以你都當我係新手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"297dc6fc55d1f0b3382036becb40074d0b92cc74","tid":428480,"uid":58266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T06:20:20.000Z","msg":"新手 TG: pieter27"},{"pid":"a648fe7749fc78b697558cb453acab1536de082b","tid":428480,"uid":58266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T06:20:20.000Z","msg":"新手 TG: pieter27"},{"pid":"d84febadc41fbc333f417d81f8c0c92de41fa78d","tid":428480,"uid":117146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T06:25:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>pt 左\\右翼ok?<br />\n<br />\n我本身打開cdm，但想練下打翼，所以你都當我係新手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n無問題. <br />\nTG?"},{"pid":"429c7fc05dadda084b736e295be6923e54a00872","tid":428480,"uid":117146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":